            . I am an officer. I was sent for, and took the prisoner.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was coming down Shoreditch on that morning - a young man came and told me to go and ask 11s. for it, and they would not give it - then he told me to go on further, and I went to this house - he gave me 10s. for it - we changed half a sovereign and had half a pint of beer; I told them to go there, but I do not know whether they went or not.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290910-213-person1968">
                  GEORGE 
                  MATTHEW MILLER
               <interp inst="t18290910-213-person1968" type="surname" value="MATTHEW MILLER"></interp>
