                     <interp inst="t18290910-213-person1968" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I offered him 10s. - he went home with me, I gave him half a sovereign - he said he understood it was half a guinea - he went away, and came again and said it was a great sacrifice, but he would let me have it.</p>
